source.name: Community Health Survey (GIS data) 2004_2008
source.description: Provides Community Health Survey aggregated city-wide rates by United Hospital Fund neighborhoods and two Boundaries files. These are GIS data The rates cover a number of health topics including: general health status, health care access, cardiovascular health, diabetes, asthma, immunizations, mental health, smoking, second-hand smoke, obesity, commuting patterns, physical activity, cancer screening, HIV, sexual behavior, birth control, drug use, and domestic violence.
